OL,3,CCampaigners lose legal bid over
OL,4,Cclosure of disability day centres
OL,6,FFamilies affected by the closure of
OL,7,Fday centres for people with
OL,8,Fdisabilities in Birmingham have lost a
OL,9,Flegal battle with the city council and
OL,10,Fits lead commissioner, who is
OL,11,Foverseeing #300 million in cuts.
OL,13,FMax Caller, referred to by campaigners
OL,14,Fas "Max the Axe", blocked an attempt
OL,15,Fby councillors to scrutinise the
OL,16,Fcontroversial decision to shut four
OL,17,Fday centres: Beeches GOLDD, Fairway,
OL,18,FHarborne, and Heartlands.
OL,26,@vD@DOUvD@PO]
