OL,3,CCampaigners lose legal bid over
OL,4,Cclosure of disability day centres
OL,6,FThe closures were part of a wider
OL,7,Feffort to address a #1.95 million
OL,8,Fbudget gap for 2024`25 and #3.35
OL,9,Fmillion in 2025`26.
OL,11,FFollowing the cabinet's decision to
OL,12,Fclose the centres, six councillors
OL,13,Fsought to have it reviewed by a
OL,14,Fscrutiny committee through the formal
OL,15,F"call-in" process.
OL,17,FBut Max Caller, who was appointed as
OL,18,Flead commissioner after the council
OL,19,Feffectively declared bankruptcy in
OL,20,F2023, overruled them, blocking further
OL,21,Fexamination by the scrutiny committee.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@IO]
