OL,6,FHis intervention, as an unelected
OL,7,Fofficial, sparked criticism from
OL,8,Fcampaigners and some councillors, who
OL,9,Fargued that elected representatives
OL,10,Fshould have the final say.
OL,12,FHowever, a court has now ruled that
OL,13,Ffamilies will not be allowed to
OL,14,Fchallenge the decision in front of a
OL,15,Fjudge, having missed the initial
OL,16,Fdeadline to file.
OL,18,FMr Justice Eyre said: "This is an
OL,19,Facademic issue that it would not be
OL,20,Fappropriate for the court to consider.
OL,26,@zD@WOU
