OL,6,F"In my judgement, any decision on this
OL,7,Fmatter is not likely to affect a large
OL,8,Fnumber of cases.
OL,10,F"If this matter were to process, it
OL,11,Fwould take up... several days of court
OL,12,Ftime instead of cases that affect a
OL,13,Fgreat deal of people."
OL,15,FThe decision could be a signal to
OL,16,Fcommissioners embedded in councils
OL,17,Facross the country and might be seen
OL,18,Fas a boost to their power.
