OL,3,CCampaigners lose legal bid over
OL,4,Cclosure of disability day centres
OL,6,FCampaigner, Jean Cross, whose brother
OL,7,FRobert attended Harborne Day Centre
OL,8,Ffor 43 years before it closed in
OL,9,FMarch, said of Max Caller: "He's
OL,10,Fruling the roost and nobody voted for
OL,11,Fhim. He was just parachuted in by the
OL,12,Flast Government."
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News Central in
OL,15,FOctober, Max Caller defended his
OL,16,Fdecision saying: "First of all, when
OL,17,Fthe council signed up for the
OL,18,Fexceptional financial support scheme,
OL,19,Fit undertook to government that it
OL,20,Fwould use the most expeditious process
OL,21,Fto carry all the difficult decisions.
