OL,6,F"This is just one of the many
OL,7,Fdifficult decisions that the council
OL,8,Fhas to take, but it has to do them at
OL,9,Fpace."
OL,11,FHe also pointed out that the decision
OL,12,Fhad already undergone "pre-decision
OL,13,Fscrutiny," saying a review would only
OL,14,Fduplicate work that had already been
OL,15,Fdone.
OL,17,FLastly, he added: "Every month's delay
OL,18,Fcosts around #100,000, and that
OL,19,F#100,000 is other people's services,
OL,20,Fother jobs, other things that need to
OL,21,Fbe resolved."
